fell 1 to 27; Apple Computer 1\ to 38|, and Microsoft 1\ to 48}.
   The NYSE's composite index of all its listed common stocks
dropped 1.51 to 146.78. At the American Stock Exchange, the market
value index was down 1.31 at 293.49.
