<2ND_LINE>AM-Whirlpool Moves,0101</2ND_LINE>
<HEAD>Firestone President Named President At Whirlpool</HEAD>
<DATELINE>BENTON HARBOR, Mich. (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Albert E. Suter, the president of
Firestone Tire & Rubber Co., has been elected president and chief
operating officer at Whirlpool Corp., the appliance maker announced
Thursday.
   Suter, 52, will remain a member of the Whirlpool board, to which
he was elected in April, Whirlpool Chairman David R. Whitwam said.
   Suter assumes the title of president from Whitwam, who will
continue as board chairman and chief executive officer.
   Prior to joining Firestone, Suter was a vice chairman with
Emerson Electric Co.
</TEXT>
